[SIZE=5][B][COLOR=Teal]Overview[/COLOR][/B][/SIZE]

[SIZE=4]This addon [I]Clock - TST[/I] adds a completely customizable and movable label to the game which shows you the current date and time of [I]Tamriel[/I] and of Earth (linked to your system time, thus it is accurate where ever you are).
Additionally, it also shows the current state of the moon and the remaining time to the next phase.[/SIZE]

